item.title: CVE-2019-6319|2024-08-04T20:16:24.796Z -- hp%20inc. -- hp%20deskjet%203630%20all-in-one%20printer%20series
item.description: HP DeskJet 3630 All-in-One Printers models F5S43A - F5S57A, K4T93A - K4T99C, K4U00B - K4U03B, and V3F21A - V3F22A (firmware version SWP1FN1912BR or higher) have a Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF) vulnerability that could lead to a denial of service (DOS) or device misconfiguration.
